鴻。腦退化的父親，只是化了諸般色相，只是留白的地方最是動人。緊握着他的手，你在耳邊告訴他：爸爸，謝謝你，人生的妙諦，雖你都忘懷，我卻永記你的大愛，像那天我們擁有的黃昏，西天最迷人的一片雲彩。」"},{"pid":"bed197977b33b30dff385b7c702d16e1a5755492","tid":395390,"uid":3520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"香港真正有才之士越來越少，當年高錕校長，到之後教大莫禮時都係好值得尊重嘅校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家個啲奶共校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caac9c3e1acedd147aa1ae8affc9074382bc3717","tid":395390,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T23:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3d883d810595db3298a642187e1c281c03ddfb","tid":395390,"uid":37414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bbfb90236d1c1c6b92e36043af71965878581a","tid":395390,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"如果佢係而家呢個年代做校長<br />\n一被委任做港事顧問已經被連登仔屌到上天花板啦"},{"pid":"35fe5266ce63ce0a0dfd62ead37d7ef2a8f723cb","tid":395390,"uid":97626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢係而家呢個年代做校長<br />\n一被委任做港事顧問已經被連登仔屌到上天花板啦</blockquote><br />\n佢個時都比人屌到上天花板啦<br />\n只係後來佢冇實際做過啲乜姐"},{"pid":"009c5254bd704849a0efac60d7db82bfc6b31adb","tid":395390,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個唔記得自己發明過光纖攞埋Nobel都剩係記得自己老婆嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實光纖技術唔係佢發明，佢發明嘅係用光纖通訊"},{"pid":"6feefc46f46f1fda7e4cc1da682c5a0ee32de4fe","tid":395390,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"